thread.title: Andrew
thread.title_full: SJF Material Handling Inc. reviewed by Andrew

author: Andrew
title: Andrew
text:
I didn't feel that the communcation was great after the order was placed. The trucking company delivered part of the order and the remainder was "Lost". It took multiple emails by me to try and figure out where the final item was to complete my order and never did receive a definitive answer as to when it would deliver. A few days later it just showed up.
Once all items arrived, the racking worked as expected.
